---
title: Caribbean Coconut & Black Bean Curry with Garlic Rice, Charred Pineapple Salsa & Mint
description: Black beans are the star of this vegetarian main course. They're packed with fibre and protein, ideal to turn this
mildly spiced chilli into a hearty dinner, while garlic rice and a zesty tomato salsa add oodles of flavour.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
